title: Ask HN: Where to Start with Discworld?
text:
In every thread about books, Pratchett novels always come up.

With 41 books, the discussion about "Reading order" is of course often held.

Notably, I already looked at L-Space's and Discworld Emporium.

But what does HN thinks about this?
